* is an expressions , 'Hello' is a value , -87.5 is a value , - (substraction) is an expressions , / (divide) is an expressions , + (addition) is an expressions , 6 is a value
difference between string and variable -  string is made up sequence of characters. for example "hello"  ,   variable is a named location used to store data in memory, for example A = 10
